name: Neu Icons
description:
Neu is a free crisp cohesive icon set library that provides a wide range of categories. Based on 24px grid material. It brings a powerful look to your project. Created with a simple basic object, combine with other shapes, and finish with passion. 1773 icons, 2 styles, and 29 categories in total.


More detailed documentation on Github. Visit Neu Icons for more info.
